               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280110-81-cd408" type="crimeDate">24th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280110-81-off407 t18280110-81-cd408"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 2s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280110-81-victim590" type="victimName">
                        Richard Hill 
                        Sandys
                     <interp inst="t18280110-81-victim590" type="surname" value="Sandys"></interp>
